{
  "id": "RAW_6afe2976",
  "title": "AI 降本的残酷真相，你的游戏凭什么活在 AI 时代？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5OTE0NjIwNw==&mid=2247484635&idx=1&sn=54cd7b319a63a4969a0175ba3ba82368",
  "date": "2025-12-02 11:00:00",
  "author": "43 Talks",
  "siteName": "43 Talks",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:inherit;white-space-collapse:break-spaces;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\">在游戏圈里流传着一个让很多人感到透心凉的数字：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:inherit;white-space-collapse:break-spaces;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\">1%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:inherit;white-space-collapse:break-spaces;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\">。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-doc-parser=\"lark\" data-mpa-uuid=\"922e1cc44717f1a95f2825c69cedddf6\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml0mhg1fm2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-mpa-doc-parser=\"lark\" data-mpa-uuid=\"922e1cc44717f1a95f2825c69cedddf6\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml0mhg1fm2\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 []\">\n    <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw51x\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这是目前AI可能为一款商业游戏带来的利润率提升。很多人看到这个数字，第一反应是失望，觉得AI雷声大雨点小，甚至觉得这是一场骗局。</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;word-break:break-word;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">在</span></span><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1769\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-doc-parser&quot;:&quot;lark&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-uuid&quot;:&quot;922e1cc44717f1a95f2825c69cedddf6&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;miml0mhg1fm2&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space-collapse: break-spaces;font-family: LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Tahoma, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft Yahei\\&quot;, Arial, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, sans-serif, \\&quot;Apple Color Emoji\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI Emoji\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI Symbol\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Color Emoji\\&quot;;color: rgb(31, 35, 41);text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.6em;word-break: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 24px;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">由</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;word-break:break-word;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">43 College</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">、</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;word-break:break-word;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">易论AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">与</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;word-break:break-word;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">模速</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">空间</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">联合举办的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">43 Talks</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">第7期线下思辨沙龙</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;word-break:break-word;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">上，本期嘉宾AI游戏投资人</span></span><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1kvn\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-doc-parser&quot;:&quot;lark&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-uuid&quot;:&quot;922e1cc44717f1a95f2825c69cedddf6&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;miml0mhg1fm2&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space-collapse: break-spaces;font-family: LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Tahoma, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft Yahei\\&quot;, Arial, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, sans-serif, \\&quot;Apple Color Emoji\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI Emoji\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI Symbol\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Color Emoji\\&quot;;color: rgb(31, 35, 41);text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.6em;word-break: break-word;margin: 0px 0px 24px;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;miml0mgw1kvn&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(255, 169, 0);font-weight: bold;\">筱宁</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;word-break:break-word;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">选择直面这一现实。作为一位曾在游戏研发一线熬过夜、改过包的“老兵”，她像一位坦诚的老友，在现场冷静地拆解了这个数字，用这看似残酷的1%，为在场的从业者们算了一笔最真实的账。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1kvn\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;caret-color:rgb(0, 121, 214);font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mimmtmch237q\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mimmtmd35yu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">本文系43 Talks根据筱宁现场分享编辑整理</span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000973\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.56171875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c2f6d90&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVMBvibKic8DicAX5WTgCib7z0WjxNKozxv1m9mojqAo8FzZiaV1dGDFic9lkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml1emcn0f\">\n    <div style=\"padding:1px 5px;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin:5px;border-bottom-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);border-left:5px solid rgb(15, 75, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;border-top-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);line-height:32px;border-right-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);padding-right:10px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"border-color: rgb(15, 75, 235);font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml5i1in7r\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mio5nldslf6\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 18px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mio5nle63wi\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">那石破天惊的1%，从何而来？</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:24px 0px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">首先，需要明确这笔账的计算前提：它针对的是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">中大厂的长线商业化手游</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，且仅聚焦于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">研发制作</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这一环。在成熟的商业模型中，研发成本通常只占总流水的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">10%-15%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">当我们把目光收束，会发现在研发的“铁三角”——美术、程序、策划中，人类智慧依然是坚固的堡垒。特别是在最耗费心血的美术环节，那些精细的3D建模、那些能打动人心的角色动画，依然需要资深美术师一笔一笔去雕琢。AI目前能做的，更多是辅助策划与美术、程序之间的需求梳理和铺垫工作。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1vp6\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这笔账其实很清晰：AI处理了那80%只占20%成本的长尾工作，即便效率翻倍，折算下来，确实只能节省极有限的成本。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1vp6\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000974\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5592680986475735\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1257\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/TDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVlWTzpIOFGYCLIvMicvIGahOaSgibI3t9s5dibmQzOCaBRSQRr4pQCBhMQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1257\" data-cropy1=\"4.349480968858131\" data-cropy2=\"706.7906574394464\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"323\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=159e961c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVicmB3mQTiavficN1KEtfYia3dPvDjh0vXcmezmtzk2UoiaLicyrXibUSTicJ4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgwdp1\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">但这难道不是一件好事吗？</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw92n\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这个1%恰恰证明了：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: normal;\">在游戏创作中，核心的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">审美</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: normal;\">、细腻的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">情感表达</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: normal;\">、以及那种“只有人能懂人”的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">艺术直觉</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: normal;\">，是无法被廉价算力轻易稀释的。</span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw23on\"></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miml8htz1ehs\" style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml8hu0sf4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miml8mo812n8\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml8moo1los\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">我们不应该指望或惧怕AI成为那个全能的替代者去接管所有的工作。相反，它更像是一个勤恳的学徒，帮助处理掉那些繁琐、重复的边角料，好让制作人、主美，能把最宝贵的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">注意力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，留给那些真正决定游戏灵魂的“核心资产”。</span></span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml1if3x6q\">\n    <div style=\"padding:1px 5px;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin:5px;border-bottom-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);border-left:5px solid rgb(15, 75, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;border-top-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);line-height:32px;border-right-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);padding-right:10px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"border-color: rgb(15, 75, 235);font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mio5nomq23rw\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 18px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mio5nomcfpc\">既然如此，为何2024年又成了AI游戏元年？</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:24px 0px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgwnsz\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">既然现状如此骨感，为什么今天我们还要聚在这里谈论AI游戏？</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw9nl\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">因为季节变了。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1bga\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">如果说2023年是AI游戏的倒春寒，那么2024年到2025年，正在迎来新的播种期。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1ij8\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">两个变化正在发生：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1hxz\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">第一，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">成本</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">的坚冰正在融化。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;随着Token价格的快速下降，让AI应用的成本降至“平民级”，这意味着开发一款真正面向C端、追求长线留存的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">AI原生游戏</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，逐渐在商业上变得可行。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1nvd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">第二，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">立项周期</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">的更替。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;很多2021年前立项的游戏其底层框架早已定型，那是旧时代的产物，AI只能作为补丁锦上添花，而现在，游戏行业正进入2024-2025的新一轮立项周期。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgwc8u\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">今天的制作人，思考的不再是如何把AI塞进旧流程，而是必须回答一个关乎3年后生死存亡的问题：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“我的下一款产品，要如何基于AI从零开始构建？”</span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw12xg\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">从修补匠到建筑师的角色转变，推动整个游戏行业开始探索AI的原生应用。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml1ky25s3\">\n    <div style=\"padding:1px 5px;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin:5px;border-bottom-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);border-left:5px solid rgb(15, 75, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;border-top-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);line-height:32px;border-right-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);padding-right:10px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"border-color: rgb(15, 75, 235);font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml9th62195\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miml9w3aikj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 18px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml9w3n1bg7\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">寻找AI时代的《愤怒的小鸟》</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:24px 0px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw10ab\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">那么，当不再执着于那1%的利润，AI究竟能带来什么？</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1zfj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">打一个比方。现在的我们，就像处在《愤怒的小鸟》诞生前夜的触屏时代。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw5r\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">当年，触屏技术刚出来时，大家只是觉得点屏幕比按键盘方便一点。直到《水果忍者》和《愤怒的小鸟》出现，将“划动”和“拖拽”变成了核心乐趣，大家才恍然大悟：原来技术可以这样玩。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1ext\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">AI也是一样。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1boc\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">现在的Token价格已经降到了“平民级”，这不仅仅是成本的降低，更是创造门槛的“民主化”。这意味着，AI不再是昂贵的奢侈品，而变成了肥沃的土壤。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw1aiu\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">在这片土壤上，我们有机会种出全新的物种：</span></span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6em;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgweig\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">也许不再是冷冰冰的NPC，而是能记住你生日、懂你喜怒哀乐的数字伙伴；</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw9ph\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">也许不再是千篇一律的脚本，而是一个会根据你的选择动态生长的活的世界。</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw14sj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这种体验，不是为了省钱，而是为了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">连接</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw10bw\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">当玩家可以和一个拥有记忆、情商在线的AI角色进行一场真正的对话时，这种被理解、被陪伴的感觉，才是技术变革赋予的最大礼物。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000979\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5591739475774424\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1259\" style=\"display: inline-block;object-fit: contain;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/TDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVOIcnqtmtufbNEHWIghFhk8iaDG9258wQK2ZibicWP6Y8mbicN4FDia96brQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1259.8203799654577\" data-cropy1=\"6.538860103626944\" data-cropy2=\"710.5561312607946\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"323\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c4070ef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVeP2JgNKmjfOgDQabel6p2QuVtibec9YnL33xguHNVUYe7shzLHWWoQQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miml1nw9mwf\">\n    <div style=\"padding:1px 5px;font-size:14px;white-space:normal;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"margin:5px;border-bottom-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);border-left:5px solid rgb(15, 75, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;border-top-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);line-height:32px;border-right-color:rgb(15, 75, 235);padding-right:10px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p style=\"border-color: rgb(15, 75, 235);font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" leaf=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 18px;\">做时间的长期主义者</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:24px 0px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw19q7\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">对技术进步保持“谨慎乐观”。短期内不要高估AI的全能性，长期内不要低估它的颠覆性。归根结底，游戏是产品，核心在于能否利用新技术超越用户的预期。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000978\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5621019108280255\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1256\" style=\"display: inline-block;object-fit: contain;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/TDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVDYmlvbjXjibDDldcEApUe5ics0kEibPOoiancSWRXZYdibRuXBFXHaEChZQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1256.6366782006921\" data-cropy2=\"706.8581314878893\" data-backw=\"576\" data-backh=\"324\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2d1ae88&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aV4m2vX2cyDgWico84v43gkNSvSgwWeiagXcqJ03gKDHJ89meibLBTPPdyQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"miml0mgw365\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">所以，亲爱的游戏人们，别再被那1%的账困扰了。它只能解释过去，定义不了未来。技术从来不是为了把人变成机器，而是为了把人从机器般的劳动中解放出来，去追寻更纯粹的乐趣。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"325\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/TDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVmS46N3BH19micFjksggMibV4qH8b6oTZGrKwBXH3EN4MnPrmaJDX6iajw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1650.433734939759\" data-cropy1=\"5.710843373493976\" data-cropy2=\"933.722891566265\" data-imgfileid=\"100000980\" data-ratio=\"0.56171875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"display: inline-block;object-fit: contain;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f37e1f18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVAuPicBz8WINMzVevgt7R4AVEMFiagbgCg4T0A1Mfu2XhQyibvUDibIwrXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"white-space-collapse:break-spaces;margin:0px 0px 24px;word-break:break-word;font-size:16px;font-family:LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;line-height:1.6em;min-height:20px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">想要了解更多关于AI游戏现状及未来的深度内容，请关注筱宁的播客</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">《</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-doc-parser&quot;:&quot;lark&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-uuid&quot;:&quot;922e1cc44717f1a95f2825c69cedddf6&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;miml0mhg1fm2&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space-collapse: break-spaces; font-family: LarkHackSafariFont, LarkEmojiFont, LarkChineseQuote, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Tahoma, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft Yahei\\&quot;, Arial, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, sans-serif, \\&quot;Apple Color Emoji\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI Emoji\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI Symbol\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Color Emoji\\&quot;; color: rgb(31, 35, 41); text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6em; word-break: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 24px; min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">405游局</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">》</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100000986\" data-ratio=\"0.5038314176245211\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1566\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aee62490&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FTDgwnHxZMLTx1eRoS0uALKRYJ83RC8aVK9THwhRibic4NqVZjl6dic6o6B4M9lZia3W585UmsR6CnqRVCE6WZOURaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度分析 AI 对游戏行业降本的真实影响，指出短期内 AI 贡献有限，但长期将重塑游戏体验，呼吁游戏人以 AI 原生思维进行产品创新。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度分析 AI 对游戏行业降本的真实影响，指出短期内 AI 贡献有限，但长期将重塑游戏体验，呼吁游戏人以 AI 原生思维进行产品创新。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了 AI 对游戏行业的实际影响，挑战了 AI 能够大幅降低成本的普遍认知。作者通过对中大厂长线商业化手游研发环节的分析，指出 AI 目前对利润率的提升仅为约 1%。这主要是因为 AI 主要处理的是长尾、低成本的辅助性工作，而核心的艺术创作和情感表达仍高度依赖人类智慧。然而，文章强调，随着 Token 价格的快速下降和新一轮游戏立项周期的到来，游戏行业应从“AI 修补匠”转变为“AI 建筑师”，思考如何基于 AI 从零开始构建原生游戏产品。AI 的真正价值在于创造全新的、超越用户预期的互动体验，例如拥有记忆和情商的数字伙伴，从而实现人与数字世界的深度“连接”，而非仅仅追求成本节约。文章呼吁游戏开发者对 AI 保持“谨慎乐观”，着眼长期主义，回归创造“好玩”的初心。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 对游戏研发的直接降本贡献目前仅约 1%。",
      "explanation": "AI 主要处理游戏研发中成本占比较小的长尾辅助工作，核心艺术创作和情感表达仍需人类，导致短期内 AI 在利润提升上表现有限。"
    },
    {
      "point": "游戏行业需从“AI 修补匠”转变为“AI 建筑师”。",
      "explanation": "随着 AI 成本降低和新立项周期，游戏制作人应思考如何基于 AI 从零开始构建原生游戏，而非仅将 AI 作为旧流程的补丁。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 的真正价值在于创造“连接”而非单纯“降本”。",
      "explanation": "AI 能带来全新的互动体验，如拥有记忆和情商的智能 NPC，通过提供个性化和情感互动，实现玩家与数字世界的深度“连接”，超越用户预期。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "揭开 AI 降本 1%的真相，不是为了泼冷水，而是为了让游戏人放下被替代的焦虑，回归创造'好玩'的初心。",
    "AI 处理了那 80%只占 20%成本的长尾工作，即便效率翻倍，折算下来，确实只能节省极有限的成本。",
    "我们不应该指望或惧怕 AI 成为那个全能的替代者去接管所有的工作。相反，它更像是一个勤恳的学徒，帮助处理掉那些繁琐、重复的边角料，好让制作人、主美，能把最宝贵的注意力，留给那些真正决定游戏灵魂的'核心资产'。",
    "今天的制作人，思考的不再是如何把 AI 塞进旧流程，而是必须回答一个关乎 3 年后生死存亡的问题：'我的下一款产品，要如何基于 AI 从零开始构建？'",
    "短期内不要高估 AI 的全能性，长期内不要低估它的颠覆性。归根结底，游戏是产品，核心在于能否利用新技术超越用户的预期。"
